item.title: Imperial Wolverines hold onto southern dodgeball title and unbeaten first team record
item.author: Filip Sebest,
item.description: The University Dodgeball League concluded this weekend with Imperial Wolverines 1s retaining the University League South title. Wolverines 1s managed to finish the season unbeaten.
